data.description: Rare five bedroom home in a great location! Owner states that sewer lines, roof, gutter, central air, furnace are recent. Square footage larger than what is listed on the tax district. Modified kitchen to serve as a chef's workspace. Kitchen includes granite countertops, stainless steel prep stations, roomy pantry, six burner Viking gas range, and breakfast area.  Five full bedrooms, one with flex space for a study, nursery, or sitting area. Oversized primary suite. Two car garage and spacious backyard. 2023-10-16
